Package it.polimi.ingsw.am11.network.RMI.client.game

Class ClientConnectorImpl

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.am11.network.RMI.client.game.ClientConnectorImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
ClientGameConnector
public class ClientConnectorImpl extends Object implements ClientGameConnector
This class is the implementation of the ClientGameConnector interface. It is used to send commands to the server through RMI.

The class is used by the ClientRMI class to send commands to the server. The class uses a ClientGameUpdatesInterface to send game updates to the server. The class uses a ClientChatInterface to send chat messages to the server. The class uses a ClientChatConnectorImpl to send chat messages to the server. The class uses a ClientViewUpdater to update the view. The class uses a ExceptionThrower to throw exceptions. The class uses an AtomicReference to store the nickname of the player. The class uses a Future to store the last command sent to the server. The class uses a ExecutorService to execute commands. The class uses a Logger to log messages.

      public static void start()
